data.description: Move-In ready well maintained 6 bedrooms, 3.5 bath walk-out ranch with over 5,500 square feet of living space. The open floor plan on both levels of the home lends itself to family fun and entertainment. The lower level has a complete kitchen, making it perfect for an in-law suite. You will be able to create gourmet meals in this beautiful kitchen. The large primary bedroom has a bath with an oversized tub and shower, along with a walk-in closet. The main level has a screened porch completely wired for TV and entertainment. The property has 2 detached garages, making it possible to have 6 cars garage kept. The completely fenced property has 100% irrigation coverage. If you are looking for a family home that is over an acre and perfect, this is it.  A must see to fully appreciate all the details that make living comfortable. Call for your showing today!
